    "description": {
      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.classes\" data-id=\"bItuvukGHbObTApr\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Mystic</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListClasses_ctl00_LabelName\">As a standard action, you can form a telepathic link with up to six other willing creatures, allowing you to communicate telepathically at great distances. This functions as <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.spells\" data-id=\"OM40z8TakmsrvDQU\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Telepathic Bond</a>, except the duration is permanent. You can have only one telepathic bond active in this way at any given time; creating a new telepathic bond immediately ends the previous one.</span></p>",
